summary: I remember the second night in Atlanta
body:
I remember the second night in Atlanta

Taylor was talking to the crowd about the hiatus she took and what it meant for her to take that time for herself and the ENTIRE arena erupted in applause and everyone was screaming so loud in support of that.

She was so shocked and touched that we cheered for her taking care and time for herself, but @taylorswift if you ever read this or if I ever get the chance to tell you, I just want you to know that we will ALWAYS support you. And you should be able to take all the time in the world for yourself, you’ve already given so much to me and millions of other people. I always want you to put yourself and your health (mental, emotional, physical) before everything and everyone else, including us. We can wait—we’re not going anywhere. We’ll always be right there backing you up. So take all the time you need baby, we’ll be right here cheering you on for it. I’m proud of you.

Love always 💖😘

- Another Taylor
